{"tid":2429531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以前真係無諗過要承諾以後不參選嚟申請保釋","createTime":"2021-03-02T11:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T15:41:15.000Z","uid":3560,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"03fa87076af6e41d65b2c9706e5fa8cbfae4eae1","tid":2429531,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:18:52.000Z","msg":"都無諗過原來選舉都要坐三年十年終生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚心痛<br />\n<br />\n2014有獨派自決派，但選舉主任不容，以後選舉類似政綱絕跡<br />\n2019區選有人提光時五一，但2020後犯國安法，立會選舉初選區佬71後亦隻字不提<br />\n而家，原來淨係參加初選同基於基本法權利所寫嘅政綱都係犯法，並要剝奪終身參選權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d734fbba20af027fd3452276cda32957272eaecb","tid":2429531,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"所以唔好再抱有希望有希望係 走"},{"pid":"d5c2152285a26581b88f3049ccc74f7cda58c5fe","tid":2429531,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:24:45.000Z","msg":"民社記，毛e，阿布泰 佢地乜都無簽+ 無話無差別否決都告"},{"pid":"1e6f01eb62c35d9306609416e08439e645c94f45","tid":2429531,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"好撚荒謬"},{"pid":"e2df5bc2e06b4418122874c411648dbc3b4740cc","tid":2429531,"uid":42804